\s Abakholwayo kabangadeleli ilizwi lakhe
\p
\v 7 Ngakho njengoba uMoya oyiNgcwele\x + 9.8; 10.15. Seb. 1.16. 2 Sam. 23.2. Mat. 22.43.\x* esithi: Lamuhla\x + 3.15. 4.7. Hlab. 95.7-11.\x* uba lilizwa ilizwi lakhe,
\v 8 lingazenzi zibe lukhuni inhliziyo zenu, njengekucunuleni, ngosuku lokulingwa enkangala,
\v 9 lapho oyihlo bangilinga, bengihlola, basebebona imisebenzi yami okweminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + Seb. 13.18.\x*;
\v 10 ngakho ngasithukuthelela lesosizukulwana, ngathi: Bayaduha kokuphela enhliziyweni; lalaba kabazazanga indlela zami;
\v 11 ngaze ngafunga\x + 4.3,5.\x* ekuthukutheleni kwami \add ngathi\add*: Kabayikungena\f + \fk kabayikungena: \fl Gr., \fq uba bezangena.\f* ekuphumuleni kwami.
\v 12 Nanzelelani, bazalwane, hlezi kuzakuba khona loba nini phakathi komunye wenu inhliziyo embi yokungakholwa, ekuduheni kuNkulunkulu ophilayo\x + Hlab. 42.2.\x*;
\v 13 kodwa khuthazanani\x + 10.24,25.\x* insuku ngensuku, kusathiwa lamuhla, ukuze kungabi khona kini owenziwa lukhuni ngenkohliso yesono\x + Zaga 28.26. Isa. 44.20. Jer. 17.9. Roma 7.11. Efe. 4.22.\x*;
