\v 17 Kodwa ngobani athukutheliswa yibo okweminyaka engamatshumi amane? Kakusibo labo abonayo yini, abazidumbu zabo zawela enkangala\x + 1 Kor. 10.5.\x*\x + Nani 14.29.\x*?
